    "asOf": "2025-02-07",
    "date": "2025-06-05T15:12:24Z",
    "text": "No More Funding for NPR Act of 2025\n\nThis bill prohibits federal funding of National Public Radio (NPR) or any successor organization and rescinds certain funds that were provided to NPR.\n\nThe prohibition includes the payment of dues to or the purchase of programming from NPR by a public broadcast station using federal funds. The prohibition does not include funds made available to NPR during certain periods of disaster response and for the sole purpose of disseminating urgent information to protect public safety."
  },
